Get a list of tibble containing parish-level UK census data

Source: R/map_parish_stats.R
map_parish_stats.Rd

This function is a wrapper around parish_stats() that returns a list of tibbles

Usage

map_parish_stats(nomis_codes, ...)

Arguments

nomis_codes

The nomis code for the data required must be a length-one character.

...

Arguments passed to parish_stats()

Value

A list of tibbles

Examples

map_parish_stats(c("TS004", "TS001"))
